        "fields": [
          { "outputField": "message", "localRole": "confirmation synthesized after Apple's content-free 204 response" }
        ]
      },
      "note": "Exact Apple relationship-add operation. The handler returns a local count-based confirmation after 204 and silently drops non-string app_ids before requiring at least one remaining ID."
